rdf:Description.dc:title: RDA Work properties
rdf:Description.skos:note: Properties derived from RDA elements and relationship designators with the domain of RDA Work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgedAsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridged as (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that shortens the source work without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abridgementOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abridgement of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been abridged, i.e., shortened without changing the general meaning or manner of presentation of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedByWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed by (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that incorporates another work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorbedInPartByWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorbed in part by (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that incorporates part of the content of another work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorptionInPartOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorption in part of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the work that has been partially incorporated into another work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: absorptionOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is absorption of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the work that has been incorporated into another work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractedInWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracted in (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work (an abstracting and indexing service) that abstracts the contents of a source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstract of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been abstracted, i.e., abbreviated in a brief, objective manner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractsForWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstracts for (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work whose contents have been abstracted by an abstracting and indexing service.

rdf:Description.reg:name: abstractWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is abstract (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that abbreviates the source work in a brief, objective manner.

rdf:Description.reg:name: academicDegree
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has academic degree
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a rank conferred as a guarantee of academic proficiency.

rdf:Description.reg:name: accompanyingWorkRelationship
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has accompanying work relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is an augmentation of, or is augmented by, or is complemented by the work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Accompanying works include supplements, concordances, indexes, catalogues, teacherâ€™s guides, music for a motion picture, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adaptation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been modified for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAMotionPictureScreenplayWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as motion picture screenplay (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work consisting of the screenplay for a motion picture, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAMotionPictureWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as motion picture (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a motion picture based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsARadioProgramWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as radio program (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a radio program based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsARadioScriptWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as radio script (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work consisting of the script for a radio program, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAScreenplayWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as screenplay (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work consisting of the screenplay for a motion picture, television program, or video, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsATelevisionProgramWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as television program (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a television program based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsATelevisionScreenplayWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as television screenplay (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work consisting of the screenplay for a television program, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAVideoScreenplayWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video screenplay (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work consisting of the screenplay for a video, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsAVideoWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as video (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a video based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsMusicalTheatreWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as musical theatre (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical theatre work based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsOperaWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as opera (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an opera based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: adaptedAsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is adapted as (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that modifies the source work for a purpose, use, or medium other than that for which it was originally intended.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addendaToWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda to (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work to which is added brief additional material, less extensive than a supplement, but essential to the completeness of the content of the work; it is usually added at the end of the work, but is sometimes issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addendaWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is addenda (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that consists of brief additional material, less extensive than a supplement, but essential to the completeness of the text of the predominant work; it is usually added at the end of the content, but is sometimes issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: addressee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has addressee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body to whom a work or part of a work is addressed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: analysedInWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysed in (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that examines the source work to identify its components and their relations.

rdf:Description.reg:name: analysisOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is analysis of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been examined to identify its components and their relations.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellant
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person or corporate body who appeals a lower court's decision.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellantCorporateBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellant corporate body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a corporate body who appeals a lower court's decision.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellantPerson
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellant person
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person who appeals a lower court's decision.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appellee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person or corporate body against whom an appeal is taken.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appelleeCorporateBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellee corporate body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a corporate body against whom an appeal is taken.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appelleePerson
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has appellee person
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person against whom an appeal is taken.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appendixToWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appendix to (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is augmented by another work that consists of material that is not essential to the completeness of the content, such as a list of references, statistical tables, and explanatory matter; the augmenting work can either come at the end of the content, or be issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: appendixWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is appendix (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that forms an augmenting part of another work which is not essential to the completeness of the content, such as a list of references, statistical tables, and explanatory matter; it can either be material which comes at the end of the content of the predominant work, or be issued separately.

rdf:Description.reg:name: architect
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has architect
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating an architectural design, including a pictorial representation intended to show how a building, etc., will look when completed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: artist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has artist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a work by conceiving, and often implementing, an original graphic design, drawing, painting, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: augmentationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is augmentation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work whose content is added to by another work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: augmentedByWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is augmented by (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that adds to the content of a predominant work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: author
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has author
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a work that is primarily textual in content, regardless of media type (e.g., printed text, spoken word, electronic text, tactile text) or genre (e.g., poems, novels, screenplays, blogs).
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Use also for persons, etc., creating a new work by paraphrasing, rewriting, or adapting works by another creator if the modification has substantially changed the nature and content of the original or changed the medium of expression.

rdf:Description.reg:name: basedOnWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is based on (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the source for a derivative work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: basisForLibrettoWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is basis for libretto (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that consists of the text of an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio, based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cadenzaComposedForWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cadenza composed for (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work such as a concerto for which an ornamental passage for a soloist has been composed, either by the same or a different composer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cadenzaWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is cadenza (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work consisting of an ornamental passage for a soloist, added to a musical work such as a concerto, either by the same or a different composer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: cartographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has cartographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a map, atlas, globe, or other cartographic work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: catalogueOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is catalogue of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for a catalogue, i.e., a complete enumeration of items arranged systematically.

rdf:Description.reg:name: catalogueWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is catalogue (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that consists of a complete enumeration of items arranged systematically.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has choreographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a work of movement.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographyForWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choreography for (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for a derivative work consisting of dance.

rdf:Description.reg:name: choreographyWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is choreography (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work consisting of dance based on the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryInWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentary in (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that contains a set of explanatory or critical notes on the described work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: commentaryOnWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is commentary on (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for a set of explanatory or critical notes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: compiler
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has compiler
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a new work (e.g., a bibliography, a directory) by selecting, arranging, aggregating, and editing data, information, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: complementedByWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is complemented by (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work paired with another work without either work being considered to predominate.

rdf:Description.reg:name: composer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has composer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a musical work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: concordanceToWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is concordance to (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for a concordance, i.e. an index of all the words in the predominant work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: concordanceWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is concordance (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that consists of an index of all the words in the predominant work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: consultant
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has consultant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body who provides consultation services, and often makes recommendations, for another person, family or corporate body that is represented as the creator of a work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containedInWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is contained in (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a larger work of which the work is a discrete component.

rdf:Description.reg:name: containerOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is container of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is a discrete component of a larger work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuationInPartOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continuation in part of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that split into two or more separate works with new titles.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continuation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the work that is continued by the content of a later work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuedByWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continued by (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work whose content continues an earlier work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: continuedInPartByWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is continued in part by (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work part of whose content separated from an earlier work to form a new work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: coordinatesOfCartographicContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has coordinates of cartographic content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a mathematical system for identifying the area covered by the cartographic content of a resource.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Coordinates may be expressed by means of longitude and latitude on the surface of planets or by the angles of right ascension and declination for celestial charts.

rdf:Description.reg:name: courtGoverned
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has court governed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a court governed by court rules, regardless of their official nature (e.g., laws, administrative regulations).

rdf:Description.reg:name: coverageOfTheContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has coverage of the content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the chronological or geographic coverage of the content of a resource.

rdf:Description.reg:name: creator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has creator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for the creation of a work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: critiquedInWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is critiqued in (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that contains a critical evaluation of the described work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: critiqueOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is critique of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for a critical evaluation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dateOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has date of work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the earliest date associated with a work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicatee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dedicatee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body to whom a work is dedicated.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dedicator
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dedicator
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body by whom a work is dedicated.

rdf:Description.reg:name: defendant
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has defendant
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person or corporate body who is accused in a criminal proceeding or sued in a civil proceeding.

rdf:Description.reg:name: degreeGrantingInstitution
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has degree granting institution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a corporate body granting an academic degree.

rdf:Description.reg:name: degreeSupervisor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has degree supervisor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person overseeing a higher-level academic degree.

rdf:Description.reg:name: derivativeWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is derivative (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is a modification of a source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: derivativeWorkRelationship
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has derivative work relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is based on or is a derivative of the work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Derivative works include summaries, abstracts, digests, adaptations, dramatizations, novelizations, screenplays, free translations, paraphrases, imitations, parodies, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: describedInWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is described in (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that describes a described work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: descriptionOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is description of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work described by a describing work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: descriptiveWorkRelationship
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has descriptive work relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is described in or is a description of the work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Descriptive works include descriptions, critiques, evaluations, reviews, commentaries, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: designer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has designer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a design for an object.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digestOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digest of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been digested, i.e., systematically and comprehensively condensed.

rdf:Description.reg:name: digestWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is digest (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that systematically and comprehensively condenses the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: director
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance, a radio or television program, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: directorOfPhotography
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has director of photography
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body that captures images, either electronically or on film or video stock, and often selects and arranges the lighting.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The director of photography for a movie is also called the chief cinematographer.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dissertationOrThesisInformation
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has dissertation or thesis information
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to information about a work presented as part of the formal requirements for an academic degree.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dramatizationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dramatization of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as a drama.

rdf:Description.reg:name: dramatizedAsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is dramatized as (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a dramatic work adapted from the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: enactingJurisdiction
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has enacting jurisdiction
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a jurisdiction enacting a law, regulation, constitution, court rule, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: epoch
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has epoch
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an arbitrary moment in time to which measurements of position for a body or orientation for an orbit are referred.

rdf:Description.reg:name: equinox
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has equinox
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to one of two points of intersection of the ecliptic and the celestial equator, occupied by the sun when its declination is 0Â°.

rdf:Description.reg:name: errataToWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is errata to (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is augmented by a list of errors in the predominant work, discovered after publication, with their corrections.

rdf:Description.reg:name: errataWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is errata (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work consisting of errors discovered after the publication of the predominant work, with their corrections.

rdf:Description.reg:name: evaluatedInWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is evaluated in (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that examines or judges the described work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: evaluationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is evaluation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is examined or judged.

rdf:Description.reg:name: expandedAsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is expanded as (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that enlarges upon the content of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: expandedVersionOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is expanded version of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for a derivative work that enlarges upon the content of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: expressionOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has expression of work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a realization of a work in the form of alpha-numeric, musical or choreographic notation, sound, image, object, movement, etc., or any combination of such forms.

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has film director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a director responsible for the general management and supervision of a filmed performance.

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmmaker
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has filmmaker
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating an independent or personal film.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: A filmmaker is individually responsible for the conception and execution of all aspects of the film.

rdf:Description.reg:name: filmProducer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has film producer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a producer responsible for most of the business aspects of a film.

rdf:Description.reg:name: findingAidForWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is finding aid for (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an archival collection that is described in a finding aid, i.e., a guide to the organization, arrangement, and contents of the collection.

rdf:Description.reg:name: findingAidWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is finding aid (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that provides a guide to the organization, arrangement, and contents of an archival collection.

rdf:Description.reg:name: formOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has form of work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a class or genre to which a work belongs.

rdf:Description.reg:name: freelyTranslatedAsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is freely translated as (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work created by freely translating the source work into another language, preserving the spirit of the original, but not its linguistic details.

rdf:Description.reg:name: freeTranslationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is free translation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been translated freely, preserving the spirit of the original, but not its linguistic details.

rdf:Description.reg:name: grantingInstitutionOrFaculty
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has granting institution or faculty
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an institution or faculty conferring an academic degree on a candidate.

rdf:Description.reg:name: guideToWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is guide to (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is augmented by another work consisting of material to help the user of the predominant work, such as notes, learning and study aids, exercises, problems, questions and answers, instructor or student materials, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: guideWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is guide (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that guides a user through the use of the predominant work, using notes, learning and study aids, exercises, problems, questions and answers, instructor or student materials, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: historyOfTheWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has history of the work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to information about the history of a work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: honouree
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has honouree
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body honoured by a work (e.g., the honouree of a festschrift).

rdf:Description.reg:name: hostInstitution
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has host institution
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a corporate body hosting the event, exhibit, conference, etc., which gave rise to a work, but having little or no responsibility for the content of the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: identifierForTheWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has identifier for the work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a character string uniquely associated with a work, or with a surrogate for a work (e.g., an authority record).
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The identifier serves to differentiate that work from other works.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustrationsForWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illustrations for (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is augmented by pictorial content designed to explain or decorate it.

rdf:Description.reg:name: illustrationsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is illustrations (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work consisting of pictorial content designed to explain or decorate the augmented work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: imitatedAsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is imitated as (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that copies the style or content of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: imitationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is imitation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work whose style or content is copied in a derivative work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: incidentalMusicForWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is incidental music for (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work such as a play or other spoken work for the stage that uses the musical work as incidental music.

rdf:Description.reg:name: incidentalMusicWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is incidental music (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work that provides the incidental music for a play or other spoken work for the stage.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexedInWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is indexed in (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work (an abstracting and indexing service) that indexes the contents of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexingForWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is indexing for (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work whose contents have been indexed by an abstracting and indexing service.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexToWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is index to (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for an index, i.e., a systematic, alphabetical guide to the contents of the predominant work, usually keyed to page numbers or other reference codes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: indexWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is index (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that provides a systematic, alphabetical guide to the contents of the predominant work, usually keyed to page numbers or other reference codes.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inSeries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is in series
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work in which the part has been issued; the title of the larger work appears on the part.

rdf:Description.reg:name: intendedAudience
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has intended audience
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the class of user for which the content of a resource is intended, or for whom the content is considered suitable.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The class of user is defined by age group (e.g., children, young adults, adults), educational level (e.g., primary, secondary), type of disability, or another categorization.

rdf:Description.reg:name: interviewee
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has interviewee
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a work by responding to an interviewer, usually a reporter, pollster, or some other information gathering agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: interviewer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has interviewer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a work by acting as an interviewer, reporter, pollster, or some other information gathering agent.

rdf:Description.reg:name: inventor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has inventor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a new device or process.

rdf:Description.reg:name: issuingBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has issuing body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family or corporate body issuing a work, such as an official organ of the body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: judge
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has judge
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person who hears and decides on legal matters in court.

rdf:Description.reg:name: jurisdictionGoverned
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has jurisdiction governed
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a jurisdiction governed by a law, regulation, etc., that was enacted by another jurisdiction.

rdf:Description.reg:name: key
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has key
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the set of pitch relationships that establishes the tonal centre, or principal tonal centre, of a musical work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Key is indicated by its pitch name and its mode, when it is major or minor.

rdf:Description.reg:name: landscapeArchitect
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has landscape architect
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an architect responsible for creating landscape works.

rdf:Description.reg:name: librettist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has librettist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an author of the words of an opera or other musical stage work, or an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: librettoBasedOnWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto based on (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for the text of an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: librettoForWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto for (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work such as an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio, that uses the text of the related work as a libretto.

rdf:Description.reg:name: librettoWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is libretto (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that provides the text of an opera or other work for the musical stage, or an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: longitudeAndLatitude
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has longitude and latitude
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a system for identifying the area covered by the cartographic content of a resource using longitude of the westernmost and easternmost boundaries and latitude of the northernmost and southernmost boundaries.

rdf:Description.reg:name: lyricist
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has lyricist
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an author of the words of a popular song, including a song or songs from a musical.

rdf:Description.reg:name: manifestationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has manifestation of work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a physical embodiment of an expression of a work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: medium
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has medium
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person held to be a channel of communication between the earthly world and a world of spirits.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mediumOfPerformance
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has medium of performance
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the instrument, instruments, voice, voices, etc., for which a musical work was originally conceived.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mergedToFormWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is merged to form (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work which brings the work together with another work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: mergerOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is merger of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to one of the works which come together to form the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureAdaptationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture adaptation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureMusicWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture music (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work that is used in a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureScreenplayBasedOnWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture screenplay based on (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as the screenplay for a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: motionPictureScreenplayWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is motion picture screenplay (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that provides the text for a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalSettingOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical setting of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that provides the text for a non-dramatic musical work, other than an oratorio.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalSettingWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical setting (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a non-dramatic musical work, other than an oratorio, that uses the text of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalTheatreAdaptationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical theatre adaptation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as a musical theatre work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalVariationsBasedOnWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical variations based on (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work from which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material is taken to form a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicalVariationsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is musical variations (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work in which melodic, thematic, or harmonic material is taken from the source work to form a discrete theme, which is repeated one or more times with subsequent modifications.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForMotionPictureWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for motion picture (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that uses the musical work in a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForRadioProgramWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for radio program (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that uses the musical work in a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForTelevisionProgramWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for television program (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that uses the musical work in a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForVideoWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for video (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that uses the musical work in a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicForWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music for (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work such as a motion picture, play, television program, etc. that uses the musical work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: musicWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is music (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work that is used in a motion picture, play, television program, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: natureOfTheContent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has nature of the content
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the specific character of the primary content of a resource (e.g., legal articles, interim report).

rdf:Description.reg:name: novelizationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is novelization of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as a novel.

rdf:Description.reg:name: novelizationWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is novelization (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a novel adapted from the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numberingOfPart
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numbering of part
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a designation of the sequencing of a part or parts within a larger work. numbering of part may include a numeral, a letter, any other character, or the combination of these with or without an accompanying caption (volume, number, etc.) and/or a chronological designation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: numericDesignationOfAMusicalWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has numeric designation of a musical work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a serial number, opus number, or thematic index number assigned to a musical work by a composer, publisher, or a musicologist.

rdf:Description.reg:name: operaAdaptationOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is opera adaptation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as opera.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherDistinguishingCharacteristicOfTheWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other distinguishing characteristic of the work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a characteristic other than form of work, date of work, or place of origin of the work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: It serves to differentiate a work from another work with the same title or from the name of a person, family, or corporate body.

rdf:Description.reg:name: otherPFCWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has other person, family, or corporate body associated with a work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body associated with a work other than as a creator.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Includes persons, etc., to whom correspondence is addressed, persons, etc., honoured by a festschrift, directors, cinematographers, sponsoring bodies, production companies, institutions, etc., hosting an exhibition or event, etc

rdf:Description.reg:name: paraphrasedAsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is paraphrased as (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that restates the content of the source work in a different form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: paraphraseOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is paraphrase of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for a paraphrase, i.e., a restating of the content of the source work in a different form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: parodiedAsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is parodied as (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that imitates the style or content of the source work for comic effect.

rdf:Description.reg:name: parodyOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is parody of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work whose style or content is imitated for comic effect.

rdf:Description.reg:name: photographer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has photographer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a photographic work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: placeOfOriginOfTheWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has place of origin of the work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the country or other territorial jurisdiction from which a work originated.

rdf:Description.reg:name: plaintiff
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has plaintiff
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person or corporate body who brings a suit in a civil proceeding.

rdf:Description.reg:name: plaintiffCorporateBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has plaintiff corporate body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a corporate body who brings a suit in a civil proceeding.

rdf:Description.reg:name: plaintiffPerson
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has plaintiff person
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person who brings a suit in a civil proceeding.

rdf:Description.reg:name: praeses
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has praeses
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person who is the faculty moderator of an academic disputation, normally proposing a thesis and participating in the ensuing disputation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: precededByWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is preceded by (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that precedes (e.g., is earlier in time or before in a narrative) the succeeding work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: preferredTitleForTheWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has preferred title for the work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the title or form of title chosen to identify the work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The preferred title is also the basis for the authorized access point representing that work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: prequel
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is prequel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that extends the narrative of an earlier work backwards in time.

rdf:Description.reg:name: prequelTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is prequel to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work whose narrative is extended backwards in time by the later work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: producer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has producer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for most of the business aspects of a production for screen, sound recording, television, webcast, etc.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: The producer is generally responsible for fund raising, managing the production, hiring key personnel, arranging for distributors, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: productionCompany
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has production company
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a corporate body that is responsible for financial, technical, and organizational management of a production for stage, screen, sound recording, television, webcast, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: programmer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has programmer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body responsible for creating a computer program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: radioAdaptationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio adaptation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: radioDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has radio director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a director responsible for the general management and supervision of a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: radioProducer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has radio producer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a producer responsible for most of the business aspects of a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: radioProgramMusicWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio program music (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work that is used in a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: radioScriptBasedOnWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio script based on (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as the script for a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: radioScriptWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is radio script (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that provides the text for a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: relatedWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has related work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work, represented by an identifier, an authorized access point, or a description, that is related to the work being described (e.g., an adaptation, commentary, supplement, sequel, part of a larger work).

rdf:Description.reg:name: remadeAsWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remade as (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a new motion picture, radio program, television program, or video based on an earlier work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: remakeOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is remake of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for a new motion picture, radio program, television program, or video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacedByWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replaced by (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a later work used in place of an earlier work, usually because the later work contains updated or new information that makes the earlier work obsolete.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacedInPartByWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replaced in part by (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a later work used in part in place of an earlier work, usually because the later work contains updated or new information that makes part of the earlier work obsolete.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacementInPartOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replacement in part of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an earlier work whose content has been partially replaced by a later work, usually because the later work contains updated or new information that makes the earlier work obsolete.

rdf:Description.reg:name: replacementOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is replacement of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an earlier work whose content has been replaced by a later work, usually because the later work contains updated or new information that makes the earlier work obsolete.

rdf:Description.reg:name: respondent
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has respondent
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a candidate for a degree who defends or opposes a thesis provided by the praeses in an academic disputation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reviewedInWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is reviewed in (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that contains a brief evaluation of the described work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: reviewOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is review of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for a brief evaluation.

rdf:Description.reg:name: rightAscensionAndDeclination
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has right ascension and declination
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a system for identifying the location of a celestial object in the sky covered by the cartographic content of a resource using the angles of right ascension and declination.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayBasedOnWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay based on (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as the screenplay for a motion picture, television program, or video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForTheMotionPictureWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay for motion picture (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that uses the text as a screenplay for a motion picture.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForTheTelevisionProgramWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay for television program (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that uses the text as a screenplay for a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForTheVideoWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay for video (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that uses the text as a screenplay for a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayForWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay for (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work such as a motion picture, television program, or video, that uses the text of the work as a screenplay.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenplayWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is screenplay (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that provides the text for a motion picture, television program or video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: screenwriter
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has screenwriter
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an author of a screenplay, script, or scene.

rdf:Description.reg:name: scriptForTheRadioProgramWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is script for radio program (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that uses the text as the script for a radio program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: sculptor
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has sculptor
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to an artist responsible for creating a three-dimensional work by modeling, carving, or similar technique.

rdf:Description.reg:name: separatedFromWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is separated from (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that spun off a part of its content to form a new work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: sequel
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is sequel
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a later work that continues the narrative of an earlier work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: sequelTo
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is sequel to
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the work whose narrative is continued by the later work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: sequentialWorkRelationship
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has sequential work relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is preceded by or succeeded by the work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Sequential works include sequels, prequels, continuations, superseding works, etc.

rdf:Description.reg:name: seriesContainerOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is series container of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been issued as part of a series.

rdf:Description.reg:name: splitIntoWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is split into (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to one of two or more works resulting from the division of an earlier work into separate works.

rdf:Description.reg:name: sponsoringBody
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has sponsoring body
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a person, family, or corporate body sponsoring some aspect of a work, e.g., funding research, sponsoring an event.

rdf:Description.reg:name: stringsOfCoordinatePairs
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has strings of coordinate pairs
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a system for identifying the precise area covered by the cartographic content of a resource using coordinates for each vertex of a polygon.

rdf:Description.reg:name: subseries
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is subseries
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a serial or multipart work that consistently appears in a larger work; the title of the larger work appears on all issues or parts of the subseries

rdf:Description.reg:name: subseriesOf
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is subseries of
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work in which the part consistently appears; the title of the larger work appears on all issues or parts of the subseries.

rdf:Description.reg:name: succeededByWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is succeeded by (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that succeeds (e.g., later in time or after in a narrative) the preceding work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: summaryOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is summary of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work used as the basis for a brief recapitulation of its content.

rdf:Description.reg:name: summaryWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is summary (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that consists of a brief recapitulation of the content of the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: supplementToWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is supplement to (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is updated or otherwise complemented by the augmenting work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: supplementWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is supplement (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that updates or otherwise complements the predominant work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: systemOfOrganization
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has system of organization
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a system of arranging materials in an archival resource or a collection.

rdf:Description.reg:name: televisionAdaptationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is television adaptation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: televisionDirector
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has television director
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a director responsible for the general management and supervision of a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: televisionProducer
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has television producer
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a producer responsible for most of the business aspects of a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: televisionProgramMusicWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is television program music (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work that is used in a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: televisionScreenplayBasedOnWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is television screenplay based on (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as the screenplay for a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: televisionScreenplayWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is television screenplay (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that provides the text for a television program.

rdf:Description.reg:name: titleOfTheWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has title of the work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a word, character, or group of words and/or characters by which a work is known.

rdf:Description.reg:name: variantTitleForTheWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has variant title for the work
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a title or form of title by which a work is known that differs from the title or form of title chosen as the preferred title for the work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: verseAdaptationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is verse adaptation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as a literary composition in verse form.

rdf:Description.reg:name: verseAdaptationWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is verse adaptation (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a literary composition in verse form adapted from the source work.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoAdaptationOfWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video adaptation of (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted for video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoMusicWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video music (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a musical work that is used in a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoScreenplayBasedOnWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video screenplay based on (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that has been adapted as the screenplay for a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: videoScreenplayWork
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: is video screenplay (work)
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that provides the text for a video.

rdf:Description.reg:name: wholePartWorkRelationship
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has whole-part work relationship with
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to a work that is contained in or contains the work.
rdf:Description.skos:scopeNote: Parts of works include discrete components such as subseries, and individual poems, stories, or essays in a collection or anthology.

rdf:Description.reg:name: yearDegreeGranted
rdf:Description.rdfs:label: has year degree granted
rdf:Description.skos:definition: Relates a work to the calendar year in which a granting institution or faculty conferred an academic degree on a candidate.
